      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="17229142">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2737103/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2737103-37.jpg" alt="哈哈儿" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17229142/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17229142/" class="">第234页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2737103/" class=" " title="哈哈儿">哈哈儿</a>
                (sleeping)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="17229142">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">校对问题：
表二：
农作活动一栏：“豆打豆”，应为“打豆”吧</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-03-12 16:31</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                校对问题：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>表二：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>农作活动一栏：“豆打豆”，应为“打豆”吧
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

